data.description: Location, location, location! Live at the northwest corner of Palmer Ranch in a gated community on one of the largest private lots in the community. From the private west-facing pool, you do not see either neighbor. This three-bedroom, two-bath home even has a den. Low HOA fees of $1,500.00 annually, make this property the perfect vacation home or year-round residence. With just under 2,000 square feet, this floor plan lives so much larger. The primary bedroom overlooks the pool area with lush vegetation. The pool area has 22-by-13 feet of covered area for dining and the screened pool cage is 35-by-22. Even the garage is slightly oversized. The garage door and Lift Master were replaced in 2021, and the air conditioner was replaced in 2022. The water heater was replaced in 2023 and it has an expansion tank. The home has been repiped, the exterior irrigation system has been rebuilt and new heads were installed. The exterior has recently been repainted, and the custom front door, with leaded glass side lights, highlights the home's handsome coloration. When you enter the property from the wide foyer, your eyes are immediately drawn to the private backyard and pool. Privacy awaits you, call today!
